    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "> Benefits?\n\nI do not see any direct benefit. The only interesting part is porting our code to an import/export pattern that is now part of ECMAScript instead of relying on `require` that is not part of the language.\n\nBUT we already use things that are not part of the language (like the mighty css loading technique) so this is not true to say we only use standard things :).\n",
