  {
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Doable, but some require cannot be ported to import for now: decorators, they are placed somewhere in render() to be testable (mockable with rewire).\n\nWe can get out of it if we import on top but decorate in render with a simple guard DecoratedRefinementList = DecoratedRefinementList || decorate(RefinementList)\n",
